winx club 3d : magical adventure ( italian : winx club 3d : magica avventura ) is a ( cgi ) animated film that was released in italy on october 29 , 2010 . the film is a sequel to winx club : the secret of the lost kingdom . it was first thought to have taken place right after the fourth season . since roxy , the fairy of animals , does not appear at alfea or is mentioned in this film and nabu appears even though he died in episode 24 of season 4 , it is now thought that the film takes place sometime in the middle of season 4 .